00:25:14,511 --> 00:25:43,101
uh when it failed nothing was said at all nothing there was no um no sense of uh of even acknowledging it in a way and she went home and she did this with her husband every time her husband did something wonderful or or something that she was pleased with and she would praise him and when he did something that she didn't she didn't like she didn't say anything and of course he changed you see

215
00:25:43,688 --> 00:25:45,650
And then she very foolishly told him the trick.

216
00:25:47,152 --> 00:25:53,098
I think probably all hell let loose, because often you don't want to feel you've been manipulated.

